WEBVTT

00:14:03.342 --> 00:14:07.217
Bonobos' co-president Brad Andrews
likes to set a high bar.

00:14:07.241 --> 00:14:10.483
Brad Andrews: "Fit for every man"
is the mantra that we rally around.

00:14:10.507 --> 00:14:13.284
AG: Living by that mantra
means asking one simple question.

00:14:13.308 --> 00:14:16.894
BA: What are customers coming in
and asking for that we do not offer?

00:14:16.918 --> 00:14:20.386
TK: Oftentimes we wouldn't
be able to accommodate those

00:14:20.410 --> 00:14:23.809
that had really big quads or bigger butts,

00:14:23.833 --> 00:14:28.367
and even if we put them
in our most generously cut pant,

00:14:28.391 --> 00:14:30.039
they would still be too tight.